  "text": "Altogether 75 orthologs of eight SotubMCs were found from seven selected Solanaceae family members, and Arabidopsis, grape and rice genome database ( natural selection here suppresses protein changes. The divergence time of the SotubMCs and its orthologs from the Solanaceae members ranged from w5.3 to 45.8 MYA ( Table 2 ). The evolutionary divergence time of the SotubMCs and its orthologs was found in consistence with the species divergence time of the Solanaceae family members calculated using time tree software [CITATION_1] (Table 2) ).",
